                                <div>[2026-07-11 10:45:02 UTC] Analyzing sentiment on 3 new reviews...</div>
                                <div class="text-emerald-400">[2026-07-11 10:45:06 UTC] SUCCESS: Auto-replies published.</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
